Review text: I bought this to add some meal prep routine to a weight loss regimen. The portion sizes are actually rather sensible, the utensils are stored very well, and the leakproofing is phenomenal, even under pressure when heating up soup., "Now, on to the gripes, of which there are only three & theyre very petty;", "I would like it more if the upper compartments walls actually sealed against the lid. I commute to work by bicycle & sometimes my cargo can get jostled around, causing any liquids in the smaller compartments to mix. Perhaps including a slip-on rubber tree-gasket would help?", I also have a suggestion for the sauce containers that would prevent so much residue from being left behind, but any design details will be furnished to the manufacturer later. Sometimes I like to pour rather thick sauces over my meal, and having rectangular containers that are so thin causes so much delicious sauce to be left behind until washed. However, I will say that using silicone lids for them--instead of plastic snap lids--was a stroke of genius., Finally, I would appreciate there being some kind of collapsable handle by which to carry this box, as I dropped the first one I ordered, causing it to break. Another measure of prevention might be bordering or cornering the base & lid with rubber bumpers. This leads me into the best part of this company; the customer service., "When I broke my Linoroso Bento Box having dropped it onto a concrete floor, I emailed customer service, asking if I could buy replacement parts with a bit of help in the form of assembly instructions. By days end, they had replied, saying that they were going to ship me a replacement unit instead, and that I just had to give them the order number. The shipping of the replacement took two days, which was far faster than I expected.", "I even ordered a replacement before talking to Customer Service, so now I have three of these, and once Ive repaired the original, I plan to use them all to the fullest extent.", "Ill likely report back with pictures of the improvements Im inevitably going to make, once I come up with some."
